name: Смертельные ошибки в видеопокере: не делайте этого![Deleted 1539910605]
loanBecause:
Покер издавна считается элитной игрой истинных джентльменов. Современный ритм жизни и технологии позволяют насладиться азартом и атмосферой, не выходя из дома — в видеопокере, доступном каждому совершеннолетнему пользователю Интернета.

Как сделать игру приятной и выигрышной, избегая разочарований?

Стратегий игры существует множество, поэтому на вопрос «что сделать?» ответ будет индивидуальным и для каждого своим. Здесь мы рассмотрим, чего не надо делать, никогда и ни в коем случае. 

Если вы только начинаете свой путь в видеопокере — эти советы помогут получить удовольствие от процесса, не набив типичных шишек новичка.

Внимание на пары

Далеко не каждая пара является выигрышной и оплачиваемой. Об этом нужно помнить всегда, и особенно — при выборе замены. Самая частая и фатальная ошибка новичков — ориентирование на пустую пару при решении между флеш-дро и парными картами. 

Смело разрывайте все пары от 10-ки и младше в пользу флеша или составления пары более старшей карты. 

Переоценка двустороннего стрита

Следующий существенный промах неопытных игроков — переоценка значимости комбинации из последовательности 4 разномастных карт, которая называется двусторонним стритом-дро. Часто такая рука ассоциируется с флеш-дро, являясь на самом деле малозначимой композицией с низким коэффициентом оплаты. 

Шансы превращения ее в полноценный стрит довольно невелики, поэтому не нужно придавать им большое значение и возлагать лишние надежды.

Игра с флеш-дро

Еще одна распространенная ошибка возникает при попытке разыграть флеш-дро в высокооплачиваемую комбинацию. Типичная ситуация — когда собраны 3 старшие одномастные карты с младшими цифрами той же и другой масти. К примеру, туз, дама и валет червей плюс 6 червей и 3 пик. 

Новички сбрасывают тройку в надежде на флеш, тогда как разумнее сбросить обе младшие карты. В этом случае повышается шанс на получение одной из 3 комбинаций:

• флеш;
• флеш-роял;
• значимая пара.

Поэтому, уважаемые леди и джентльмены, не позволяйте азарту взять верх над расчетом и сохраняйте истинное британское хладнокровие, пользуясь чужим опытом ошибок!

Игра Слотов – стартует новая серия турниров в клубе 

Игра Престолов – сериал, ставший культовым. История его сюжета основана на знаменитом цикле романов Песнь Льда и Пламени, автор которого Джордж Мартин. История стала настолько известной, что к армии ее фанатов примкнуло более 20 миллионов человек. Конечно, администрация клуба не могла остаться в стороне таких событий, и только отгремели битвы 7-го сезона эпопеи, они решили организовать серию турниров, посвященную этому захватывающему рассказу о вымышленном мире. Название серии состязаний – Игра Слотов, и принимать участие в ней может каждый, выполнив несложные условия. 

Как стать участником

Чтобы принимать участие в этом соревновании, надо провести ряд несложных приготовлений. Прежде всего, зарегистрируйтесь на портале, если не сделали этого раньше. Далее – пополните счет, осуществив депозит на достаточную для турнира сумму. Рассчитывайте, что минимальные ставки принимаются от 10 рублей. Всего будет градация на три типа ставок, таких себе три лиги участников: Железный Щит, Золотой Меч и Серебряная Стрела. 

В конце каждой недели борьбы будет выделена 10-ка лидеров, которые и поделят между собой деньги и призы. Автоматы будут участвовать разные, узнать их можно по особой отметке. Ее отчетливо видно в каталоге предложений, это маленький золотой кубок, который будет размещаться в углу баннера эмулятора. Задача нашего игрового клуба – обеспечить, чтобы этот выбор был максимально большим.

Самые популярные темы и жанры  слотов
На сайт собран большой выбор игровых автоматов. Мы подвели статистику и определили, какие же темы интересуют игроков клуба больше всего. Вот результаты:

Романтика (где симуляторы окунут игроков в тематику страсти, любви и романтических чувств).
Спортивная (здесь все заядлые болельщики и фанаты футбола. Баскетбола, регби и тенниса смогут не только увидеть среди символов игроков любимых команд, но и получить щедрые призы в любимых видах спорта).
Мультфильмы, комиксы, кино, книги (каждый гэмблер сможет прочувствовать изнутри атмосферу любимого произведения и побывать среди персонажей и героев любимой истории).
Мужская и женская (слоты, в которых собраны самые любимые мужские и женские штучки: от косметики и кулинарии до гаечных ключей, гаражей и автомобилей).
Ужасы (множество вампиров, вурдалак, зомби, крови, приведений и мистических историй).
Фруктовые (яркие и красочные симуляторы, которые внесут в настроение каждого игрока бодрость и позитив).
Ретро и классика (это игровые аппараты, которые наполнены стандартными для азартных игр символами: 777, вишенки, клубнички, монеты).
Приключения (в таких игровых автоматах гэмблеры могут отправиться на корабле в далекое плаванье или улететь в космос в поисках новых галактик).

name: studygroup
loanBecause:
Книга Рекордов Гиннеса и азартные игры: а ты бы смог? 

Датой появления первой Книги рекордов Гинесса считается 1955 год. Раньше она напоминала справочник, и только потом в нее стали включать уникальные случаи. Эта знаменитая книга содержит сведения о рекордах, которые напрямую связаны с увлекательными азартными развлечениями.

Необычные записи о азартных играх среди мировых рекордов

Ювелир из Канады Леви создал наиболее дорогостоящую фишку для использования в игорном заведении. Стоимость такого предмета составила 450 000 долларов. Его изготовили из 152 грамм особого золота, тогда как обрамление было выполнено из рубинов. Весной 1991 года десять человек поделили между собой сногсшибательный джек-пот в размере 180 000 000 долларов.

В 1983 году в канадском городе Торонто зафиксировали 15 756 любителей бинго, что является мировым рекордом. В 1994 году в Великобритании на футбольном тотализаторе счастливчик выиграл ставку в размере 3 000 000 фунтов. При этом крупнейшим лотерейным выигрышем принято считать сумму величиной 390 000 000 долларов. Она была разделена двумя везунчиками в 2007 году.

Еще несколько интересных рекордов, связанных с азартом

Приведем еще ряд интересных случаев:

• В 1993 году Коллин Деври и Лесли Роббинс смогли выиграть в лотерее сумму в 111 000 000 долларов. 
• Летом 1995 года Мэддисон и Гардинер смогли заполучить основную награду лотереи в размере 2 090 000 долларов.
• В 1997 году в Вегасе один щедрый игровой автомат выдал сумму величиной в 12 000 000 долларов.
• Самым юным триумфатором покерных турниров считается Када. В возрасте 21 год ему удалось обыграть Айви и Шулльмана.
• Крупнейшее соревнование по стрип-покеру прошло в Cafe Royal в Лондоне. В нем участвовало 196 игроков.

Все эти рекорды говорят о том, насколько популярными являются азартные развлечения, и как много они способны принести.

loanBecause:
ТОП-5 исторических слотов онлайн

Желая на время оторваться от будничной суеты и виртуально погрузиться в мир невероятных эмоций и ощущений, вы просто обязаны ознакомиться с подборкой пяти самых популярных слотов на историческую тематику и среди них подобрать стоящий вариант для увлекательного и прибыльного отдыха. В частности, речь пойдет о таких легендарных играх, как:

• Columbus
• Viking Age
• Attila
• Mayan Treasures
• Egyptian Heroes

С их помощью вы совершите увлекательное путешествие во времени, сумеете лично увидеть древние цивилизации таких известных стран как Египет, Греция, а также СССР и Ближнего Востока. Становитесь свидетелем кровавых сражений смелых воинов, жестоких кровопролитных гладиаторских боев, знакомьтесь с культурой, мифологией и уставом интересующих вас цивилизаций и просто получайте удовольствие от игрового процесса.

Включайте автомат Columbus и отправляйтесь навстречу переменам

Благодаря этой онлайн-разработке вы познакомитесь с легендарным мореплавателем, который открывал новые земли и плавал по многим странам. Увлекательный сюжет, бонусные опции и высокие коэффициенты выплат – этого достаточно, чтобы приятно провести свой отдых и ощутить атмосферу того времени.

Viking Age – отличная возможность ознакомиться с традициями и особенностями повседневной жизни племен викингов, живших несколько столетий назад. Интересный сюжет увлечет вас на несколько часов, и вы надолго забудете о реальном отсчете времени.

Слот Аттила: проверьте свою удачу

После запуска этого оригинального автомата вы лично в виртуальном режиме познакомитесь с жестоким предводителем Аттилой, который искусно управлял племенами гуннов. Играйте бесплатно или на деньги и удовлетворите свою потребность в азарте.

Mayan Treasures: почувствуйте себя частью древней цивилизации

Отдохнуть от повседневных проблем и наглядно увидеть, как жили племена майя и чем они занимались на протяжении всего дня, позволит эта очень интересная разработка. Достойное техническое наполнение подкупает с первых секунд, и игровой процесс становится еще азартнее.

name: Sustainable Phosphorus Metabolism
loanBecause:
Phosphorus is an essential, finite and non-substitutable resource of life - constituting the foundation of food security for humanity. 
However, it is tremendously mismanaged by the cheap prices on the global fertilizer market and the majority of it goes to waste - causing environmental problems instead of reaping benefits.

Check out this explanatory video:
https://youtu.be/Y17HqUsaoj8?list=PLluIKHDRSQLFlmafGeY_nXigVtFWKhCEA
description:
Just as humanity consists of billions of individuals, the phosphorus challenge does too - which means EVERYONE can help. This team should stand together for nothing less than ensuring equitable food access in the future by decreasing P losses all around the world. 
Follow Reduce, Reuse, Recycle and Compost. 

This means to fund kiva loans that match the following criteria:
+ organic fertilizer and composting (NO mineral fertilizer!)
+ biodigestion and sludge reuse
+ local agriculture to market loops
+ decentralized sanitation systems (DEWATS and Ecosan) for nutrient extraction from water, ideally with (safe!) sludge reuse, composting toilets etc
+ empowerement through access to education
+ organic agricultural products and farming practices
+ vegetarian products (NO more dairy, cattle or meat which increase manure production) unless the manure is reused directly 

The list could be continued quite a bit. Please, help me updating the list/guidelines by commenting while we build up this team! :)

name: Aces of Heart - Gamblers for Good
loanBecause: Whether professional advantage players or recreational enthusiasts, we all have taken to heart a few common truths over the course of our gambling careers. We've seen that hard times can come without warning or fault. We've learned that the knowledge and support of others is an invaluable resource. And perhaps most importantly, we've discovered that while money comes and goes, investing time and resources thoughtfully and diligently will pay off in the long run. These are just some of the reasons that we choose to put a portion of our bankrolls to work for people around the globe ready to work themselves. Those familiar with the gambling community will likely not be surprised by our shared belief in humanitarianism, but given the more typical characterization of gamblers in the wider world, we like to think of these ideals as our unexpected values.
description: We are a community of gamblers whose interests and levels of experience range as widely as do our locations around the world. We are united, though, by a common belief that money is not simply a resource to be stockpiled, but a tool that can be put to work through intelligent investing and disciplined risk. It goes without saying that simply being able to think of wealth in these terms is a form of privilege, as is participating in an activity for which disposable income is a prerequisite. We are lucky to be in such a position, and - no strangers to capitalizing on luck - we are honored to take advantage of it as we partner with those who are less fortunate but no less deserving.

loanBecause:
Как и в любом современном заведении, на нашем официальном сайте ведется статистика посещений игровых симуляторов, которые чаще всего выбирают игроки. Градация ведется совершенно без привязки к бренду или сюжету. Чаще всего, игроки обращают внимание на результативность отдачи определенного симулятора, это и определяет топ лучших разработок. 

От славы труду к урокам выживания

Сейчас в первой десятке располагаются эмуляторы от Уникум, Новоматик, Игрософт и МегаДжек. Братва и Золото Партии посвящены определенному периоду в нашем регионе и обладают немалыми техническими достоинствами. Это, кроме полноценного игрового поля форматом 5Х3, еще и наличие тематических призовых игр, особенных символов с расширенным функционалом, специальных вращений. Это же можно сказать и о Книжках, Острове и хитовом автомате Ешки. Здесь также присутствует множитель выплат, игра на риск. Тематики разнообразные – Робинзон научит, как выжить на необитаемом острове, сюжет Ешек покажет, как веселятся люди в круизах. 

Больше приключений в тропиках и не только

Сюжет игры Обезьянки проведет в джунгли, а тема Жемчужины Дельфина раскроет тайну морских жителей. Единорог и Колобок посвящены легендам и сказкам, а слот Баксы научит приумножать имеющийся капитал. Технически все эти эмуляторы схожи: 

-наличие 5 барабанов; 

-специальных иконок; 

-всегда 9 линеек для поимки цепочек из символов. 

Также в каждом случае предлагается символы высшего порядка, это Вайлд и Скаттер. Первый поможет строить комбинации, второй – активирует серию спинов free-формата.
Важно и то, что присутствуют каждый раз дополнительные раунды. Обязательно – риск-игра с нетривиальным сюжетом и тематические бонус-игры. Впрочем, в  Единороге эта опция отсутствует, как и в Дельфинах, хотя компенсация также имеется – множитель выплат позволит увеличить полученные прибыли.  

Джекпоты всех топовых аппаратов довольно щедры и предлагают суммы в несколько тысяч. Это еще раз доказывает производительность моделей и оправдывает их местонахождение на вершине популярности среди аналогов в каталоге игорного портала.

name: Liberation Day

description:
Our goal is to restore freedom for the people of America and their states by limiting the federal government according to the Constitution.

I'm Eric Martin, one of this team's captains and the author of Liberation Day. Here's a description of the book:

Liberation Day—it’s a title suited to a story of a nation at war and a people held captive. In this case, the invader is not some foreign enemy. It is the government at war with the nation it governs. And the Liberation Day this book speaks of is the day we take our nation back—back from a federal government that has long defied the constitutional restraints that guarantee our freedom.

In Liberation Day, Eric Martin shows us how our Constitution can and must be used to make us and the states in which we live prosperous, powerful, and free as they were meant to be. Martin lays out a rationally innovative plan that radically downsizes or completely dissolves more than 250 federal entities that wield power both unconscionable and unconstitutional.

With its unconstitutional burdens rightfully jettisoned, our federal government will align at last with the Founding Law that makes us and our states truly free. The framers of the Constitution understood only too well that government is by its nature a beast, of use if properly restrained, but oppressive and even lethal if allowed out of bounds. By reapplying to government the well-wrought chains of our Constitution, we will liberate ourselves.

Sam Adams said it best nearly two and a half centuries ago: “It does not take a majority to prevail ... but rather an irate, tireless minority, keen on setting brushfires of freedom in the minds of men.” Here is the match. Now is the time to strike it.

A101 marketleri  özel olarak hazırlanan onlarca fırsatın bulunduğu aktüel ürün kataloglarını vatandaşlar için yayınladı. A101 29 Mart günü yüzlerce ürünü oldukça uygun fiyatlarla siz değerli müşterilerin beğenisine sunuyor.

Aile ekonomisini zor durumda bırakmadan marka ve kaliteli ürün alışveriş olanağını yaşamak isteyenlerin sıklıkla ziyaret ettiği A101 marketleri, günlük ihtiyaçların yanı sıra teknolojik alet çeşitliliğini de her geçen gün artırıyor. Hesaplı fiyatlar ile yüksek kalite ürün alışverişi yapmanızı sağlayan mağaza Türkiye’nin neresinde olursa olsun alışverişte 1 numara olmaya devam ediyor. Bir önceki kampanya döneminde olduğu gibi bu haftada oldukça büyük ses getirecek indirimlere imza atan marketler zinciri, alışverişin cazibe merkezi olmaya devam ediyor. 29 Mart A101 kampanya günlerine özel olarak yayınlanan aktüel ürün kataloglarında hangi fırsatlar yer alıyor hep birlikte inceleyelim. Oldukça hesaplı fiyatlar ile satın alım gücünü üst düzeye çıkarmak isteyenlerin ortak noktası olan ve kaliteli ürünlerin bulunduğu A101, uygun fiyatlarıyla alıcıları mutlu etmeye devam ediyor. Ülkemizin hemen her bölgesinde binlerce mağaza ile hizmetlerine devam eden ve marka ürün felsefesinden asla vazgeçmeyen A101, bu kampanya döneminde de alışverişin yükselen yıldızı olacak. Toplumda oldukça sevilen ve çok sık ziyaret edilen mağaza haline gelmeyi başaran firma, yayımladığı indirim broşürlerinde vatandaşların çoğu isteğini gerçekleştirmiş görünüyor.

loanBecause:
"The weakest
members of society should be helped to defend themselves against usury, just as poor peoples
should be helped to derive real benefit from micro-credit, in order to discourage the exploitation
that is possible in these two areas. Since rich countries are also experiencing new forms of
poverty, micro-finance can give practical assistance by launching new initiatives and opening up
new sectors for the benefit of the weaker elements in society, even at a time of general economic
downturn."
- Pope Benedict, "Caritas in Veritate", par. 65
description:
A team inspired by Catholic "montes de pieta" and guilds of the later Middle Ages and Renaissance era. Saint Matthew is the patron saint of bankers and accountants.

There are some criteria we follow in loaning:

1. We loan to women in the developing world as a way to empower women's dignity, per the research and stories found in the book "Half the Sky."

2. We loan via Kiva partners who have low interest rates, including zero-interest Islamic microfinance, because we are all brothers and sisters in Christ.

An evaluation of the ingredients contained in Ambien against those contained in safe, all natural herbal ingredients may provide more than one unpleasant surprise to those who are sure that Ambien is the best option for sleep disturbances available. In fact, Ambien can present many more long term problems than missing a couple of night's sleep ever would.
Many of those who take Ambien do not even know what a hypnotic is, let alone that there are several better options available. Zolpidem tartrate is a strong, harsh ingredient that tricks the nervous system into relaxing against its natural tendencies. By ignoring ingredients that have been shown to work with the body's natural chemistry, Ambien can only provide an extremely short term solution, since the body's natural rhythms are important for the health, mental well being and overall quality of sleep necessary to function normally.
Ambien Side Effects

Ambien comes packed with some pretty powerful potential side effects. Some side effects of Ambien are more common than others, but those who are especially sensitive to strong medications may experience some of the more rare and dangerous side effects. If side effects are a concern for you, you should consider a non-habit forming, all natural herbal sleep aid instead of Ambien.

You can expect the following common side effects: headache, vertigo, vomiting, dizziness, lethargy, cloudy mental status and confusion. Even more seriously, some of the more severe side effects associated with Ambien are changes in behavior or thought, amnesia or dependence on the product. It is not only the side effects of taking Ambien that must be considered, however. For those who become dependent on Ambien, the symptoms of withdrawal from Ambien extend from tremors to even dangerous seizures.

Does Ambien work?

Ambien does function as an extremely short term solution for sleep disturbances and other sleep issues. However, the risks associated with taking Ambien make it a much less attractive option than it first appears. Since Ambien does not work with the natural sleep cycle, it is impossible to consider for long term insomnia problems, as the body will eventually wear down and become ill without the benefit of normal sleep cycles. The main problem with Ambien, however, is the strong possibility of an addiction to the product developing.

Many people find themselves completely reliant on Ambien to sleep. Dependence on Ambien is a difficult addiction to break, and comes with many severe side effects when withdrawal kicks in. Few people are expecting to deal with a severe addiction to a prescription drug when all they were interested in was a solid night's sleep. name: Dana Turnbull Memorial Team
loanBecause: In memory of Dana Turnbull that passed on September 10th 2017. She is survived by her husband Nathan, son Alexander, sister Leah Hientz (Corey Dick), nephew Blake, parents Michael and Valerie Hientz, and numerous relatives and friends. Dana was born November 22nd 1983 in Saskatoon. A precocious child, her education was enriched through the gifted learning programs at Caswell School and Walter Murray Collegiate. Dana loved rocks. As a child, she was always collecting specimens. This translated into a career which she pursued wholeheartedly. After high school, she enthusiastically embraced her studies at the University of Saskatchewan, graduating with a Bachelor of Science in Geological Engineering. She flourished in potash mining, earning her Professional Engineering designation, and more recently she worked in oil and gas. From early childhood, Dana was passionately involved in ballet, jazz, tap, and musical theatre. To her love of dance, she brought her desire to excel and thrived in competition. Her need for adventure, balanced by her superb organizational skills, fueled her passion for worldwide travel. Meaningful relationships delighted Dana and she was blessed with many lifelong friendships. Even as an introvert, she loved social gatherings and sharing ideas and experiences with others. Dana enriched the lives of those around her with her smile, laughter, sarcasm, sass, and fierce loyalty. A dedicated wife and loving mother, Dana embraced family life. She will be sadly missed. Photos, memories and condolences may be shared with Dana’s family through www.evanjstrong.com. In lieu of flowers, memorial tributes or loans may be made directly to Kiva (www.kiva.org).

name: Friends of Chamroeun
loanBecause:
We support Chamroeun Microfinance in their mission to improve the livelihoods, skills, and self-confidence of poor families in Cambodia by providing responsible microfinance and complementary socio-economic services.

Chamroeun established in 2006 by Entrepreneurs du Monde as an NGO with a focus on serving the very poor in Phnom Penh by providing a variety of services. In 2011 they officially registered as a Microfinance Institution, and have since grown to 21 branches in 16 provinces around Cambodia.

Chamroeun aims to create an environment for the vulnerable and poorest of the poor to have access to financial services with small loan sizes adapted to their small business contexts. They also complement their financial services through a range of socio-economic services.

Their goal is the maximization of social impacts. This is accomplished through no dividend distribution, decreased product pricing, and increased product diversification to address vulnerabilities

name: Fund 17 New Orleans
loanBecause: We are based in New Orleans, a city that is experiencing an entrepreneurial renaissance yet that still maintains high levels of inequality when compared to national averages. For example, 71% of New Orleanians have sub-prime credit scores. Fund 17 believes that this figure is intrinsically tied to New Orleans's wealth and asset poverty, as it makes it difficult for anyone trying to use entrepreneurship to pull themselves out of poverty to get the funding they need. Through equitable services tailored to the needs of each micro-entrepreneur, we believe that we can help provide economic opportunity to New Orleanians who have been excluded from traditional business development services such as bank loans.
description: Fund 17 is a non-profit based in New Orleans that helps entrepreneurs in the city develop their businesses and watch their ideas come to fruition. One way we do this through one on one entrepreneurial training with our fellowship program. This program trains university students to provide assistance to entrepreneurs in the area focusing on our three key values: establishment of healthy business systems, personal goal-setting, and financial empowerment. We also serve as the Kiva ambassadors in New Orleans, meaning that we act as a resource to entrepreneurs in the area who are applying for loans.

name: Sdelat Pravilno[Deleted 1494095078]
loanBecause:
Как правильно создать вдохновение. Многие музыканты, думая, что композиции можно сочинять только от внезапно накатившего вдохновения, доходят до того, что совершенно перестают писать музыку. Существует методика, с помощью который можно вернуть продуктивность и уже к концу недели иметь около десятка годных набросков, с которыми можно будет работать.

Суть этой методики заключается в том, что Вы твёрдо решаете продолжать свою музыкальную карьеру и обещаете спустя уже семь дней иметь хотя бы наброски будущих композиций. Многие очень часто говорят себе "Я обязательно разберу этот ящик", а уже через час осознают, что разобрали максимум одну стопку бумаг, находящихся в нём. Начните разбирать свои старые демо уже сейчас, дорабатывать удачные, на Ваш взгляд, наброски и удаляя ненужные файлы.

Но основная часть методики заключается не в этом. Расскажите друзьям о том, что Вы собираетесь написать мини-альбом за неделю, сообщите об этом во всех социальных сетях — в общем, удостоверьтесь, что все запомнили Ваше высказывание и наверняка захотят упрекнуть Вас, если Вы ничего не сделаете. А слышать от знакомых "Я так и знал, что ты ничего не сделаешь" не очень приятно.

Полезно во время этой недели вести дневник, записывая туда все важные выводы, сделанные Вами по окончанию какой-то стадии написания песни и просто делиться своими мыслями, чтобы выбросить всё ненужное из головы, но при этом знать, что если что-то забудете — сможете найти это в своём дневнике.

Эта методика написания альбома хороша тем, что Вы не будете сильно напрягаться над песней, при этом продуктивность сохранится. Начинайте писать тексты каждый день. Пишите обо всём подряд, потратьте на одну песню целый день. На следующий день вернитесь к вчерашней композиции всего на тридцать минут, а затем приступайте к написанию новой песни. Такой подход помогает сохранить интерес к композиции и позволяет реализовывать несколько идей одновременно. Полезно записывать некоторые свои требования к композиции на отдельном листе, чтобы следовать им и в конце получить именно тот трек, который Вы желали создать.

При записи своих демо стоит помнить, что важнее сначала записать все партии, а потом уже редактировать дорожки и добавлять к ним эффекты. Иногда процесс эквализации какой-то партии занимает огромную кучу времени, а после этого желание продолжать работу над остальной композицией бесследно исчезает.

Для большей вероятности написания годного материала стоит выйти за рамки своих привычных записей и попробовать себя в чём-то новом. Раньше писали музыку, используя кучу плагинов и синтезаторов? Возьмите в руки гитару и попробуйте записать полностью акустический альбом — только гитара и Ваш голос. Это будет сложно, но принесёт Вам опыт работы с другими, непривычными для Вас жанрами, поможет посмотреть на композиции с другой стороны и создать что-то отличное от Вашего прошлого материала, освежить стиль. Выход за привычные рамки не всегда является неправильным решением — иногда это помогает найти что-то, что вполне сможет Вас заинтересовать.

К концу недели у Вас должно собраться около десятка песен (зависит от того, как Вы работали). Не важно, готовы ли все они полностью или являются лишь черновиками - если Вы смогли создать что-то стоящее за семь дней — Вы достигли своей цели.

Работая таким образом, Вы допишите альбом намного быстрее, не зависимо от того, как часто приходило к Вам вдохновение.

name: Ivrea Nostra con Kiva
loanBecause: Sosteniamo attraverso il microcredito di Kiva gli abitanti indigenti delle campagne dell'Africa favorendo lo sviluppo di opportunità di lavoro sul territorio locale, affinché i giovani di quelle popolazioni non siano costretti a rischiare la vita rincorrendo un futuro incerto attraverso l'immigrazione clandestina.
description:
Cinquant’anni di cooperazione per lo sviluppo dell’Africa e circa mille miliardi di dollari spesi non hanno provocato gli effetti sperati.
I sensi di colpa dell'Occidente per il passato coloniale, la corruzione endemica dei Paesi coinvolti, la sottovalutazione dei veri bisogni delle popolazioni, la debolezza contrattuale delle organizzazioni di cooperazione sono sfociati troppe volte in programmi e progetti che hanno favorito le élites al potere a scapito delle masse dei più deboli.
Anche la scuola, quasi sempre di stampo occidentale, che avrebbe dovuto formare i quadri necessari allo sviluppo, si è rivelata invece un trampolino per l'esodo dei giovani sui barconi. La mancanza di investimenti nell’industria, che non crea sbocchi occupazionali, e il rifiuto dei diplomati rispetto alle attività rurali considerate degradanti spiegano questo paradosso.
Moltissimi autori tra i quali René Dumont, il premio nobel Muhammad Yunus e Dambisa Moyo giungono a conclusioni simili.

Perché invece il microcredito, così concepito da Kiva, funziona? Perché, rispetto al dono, l'effetto si riproduce quasi all'infinito tramite i rimborsi e i reimpieghi. Perché è il prestatario e non il prestatore a decidere l'attività da intraprendere. Infine perché il rimborso stesso è la prova che l'operazione è riuscita.

La prova di quanto sopra ci è stata fornita dall’esperienza diretta: un nostro piccolo gruppo già da anni ha sperimentato il microcredito in Africa e abbiamo così aiutato circa duecento piccoli operatori rurali, uomini e donne, singolarmente o in gruppi, con risultati eccezionali: con 20 Euro si creano posti di lavoro informali.

Abbiamo così deciso di formare un team di Kiva per allargare l’esperienza  ad altre persone desiderose di contribuire al vero benessere di quel continente.

name: Flying P-Loaner
loanBecause: The "Peking" is coming home!
description:
The big Windjammers of the german shipping company F. Laeisz were called "Flying P-Liners" because they were so fast and their names always started with a "P".

Only a few of these majestic vessels survived until today, one of them is the 1911 build 4-masted barque "Peking" which has been a museum ship in New York Cities South Street Seaport since 1976. Her future was unsure as the museum was not able to finance  the urgent needet restoration. But now it is fixed that the "Peking" will be given  to Germany, get fully restored and become a part of the planned German Port Museum in Hamburg, the city where she was build and registered until 1932.

I'm so happy that this gorgeous monument of maritime history will have a future and can be visited soon again.
For celebration, I make some extra lending to "expiring soon" loans starting with a "P" and hope it will help to "safe" them, too.

Here is an unique video, taken by Irving Johnson in 1929 on the "Peking" while circumnavigating stormy Cape Horn: https://youtu.be/-DyXdx-FF8Y

And here is a clip, showing the "Peking" leaving New York at Sep. 7th 2016 for the last time: https://youtu.be/6wMRD7M911M

Further informations can be found here:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peking_(ship)
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flying_P-Liner

name: Tenderloin Economic Development Project
loanBecause: Our mission is to create and promote equitable development for the Tenderloin community in San Francisco.
description:
The borders of the San Francisco's Tenderloin have been rich with a history of art, music, and life. Over the years it has been gone through many transitions and is now is home to San Francisco’s poorest and most vulnerable residents. As one of the most affordable communities in the City, the Tenderloin has been a place where recent immigrants have been able to support their families by opening their own business with little capital but boundless energy.  Their livelihood is now threatened as San Francisco’s explosive growth is placing enormous pressure on these businesses, who have no protection again dislocation caused by increasing rents. 

We want to change that ….

Our lending team wants to assure that San Francisco remains a place where immigrants can build a future life, where small growing businesses have a chance, and where the Tenderloin neighborhood meets the needs of its residents.
KIVA’s affordable financing gives Tenderloin businesses an important tool to stabilize and grow their business so they can prosper in the new economic reality.

Through their businesses, and personally, they’ve met many fortunate (usually hard-working) people who have achieved financial independence. Does that perhaps describe you? If so, Kiva's proven approach of helping others to help themselves through small loans might be a perfect fit. A unique benefit to this form of helping others is that if you've been reluctant to donate significant sums of money because of the (not always irrational) fear that someday you, or perhaps a loved one, may need the money back, with Kiva you have that option of return. name: Fondation Tuungane
loanBecause:
The country’s labour market is badly out of balance. Demographic pressures mean that the demand for jobs is rapidly increasing while since 1990 supply has been falling steeply as a result of looting, wars and other shocks to the economy. This state of affairs has favoured the emergence of the informal sector. About 80% of the active population operate outside the labour market and the unemployment rate is 73%.

Young people face huge problems in finding work. Given the limited number of jobs on offer, the mismatch between training and the skills sought by employers, and the slow rate of retirement among public employees, more than 70% of the young are jobless. Those hardest hit are young people aged between 15 and 24 living in towns and cities. The brain drain and the crisis in the educational system mean that there is a strong demand for
expertise in human resources in the country. But foreign qualifications are more highly regarded than local ones and open the door more widely to the labour market and in particular jobs with responsibility.

Connections play a major role in finding a job in the DRC. But of the 9 000 young people leaving Congolese universities each year fewer than 100 find a job. It often happens that young graduates become street vendors, money changers, traders, operators of public telephones or security staff, for lack of any other job opportunity.

The lack of work and the absence of effective supervisory structures also push many young people into a life of crime. In Kinshasa since 2008 organised crime has developed at an alarming rate (the “Kuluna phenomenon” of serious gangster activity). In the east young unemployed people are exploited by rebel groups.

The World Bank calculates that the DRC needs to create between 2 million and 4 million jobs every year to absorb those arriving on the labour market and to reduce poverty.

Fondation Tuungane aim to enhance youth skills and visualize proper direction on the business ideas they want to pursuit in order to discrease employment crisis in Congo.
description: Fondation Tuungane is a Congolese NGO seeks to build a society where youth determines their own positive future. To do this, Fondation Tuungane catalyzes youth into action through trainings. Young people between 13 and 29 are taught different skills in business creation sothat they be able to effectively work in their communities’ settings able to create social impact projects among themselves.

description:
The Sudan Community Development Fund
 Established: 23 December 2010
 A Partnership between South Sudan and USA


 Project Description

 Background: The people of South Sudan have suffered unrelenting harsh conditions since the formulation of the nation of Sudan in the 1950’s. Since 2005, the Comprehensive Peace Agreement (signed to end the open hostilities between the North and peoples of the South has resulted in a period of relative stability and peace with the hope for sustained community-based development. In South Sudan, there have been two significant periods of civil war. Most of the hostilities took place in the south further eroding the social, economic, and emotional health of South Sudanese communities. The Arilo Center area suffers from diseases of extreme poverty (malaria, malnutrition, typhoid, cholera, etc.) and has virtually no community infrastructure (clean water, roads, electricity, communication, banking, etc are all non-existent) and confronts challenges to develop human intellectual and leadership capacity to create/enhance community development. The EFCSS - Arilo Center serves the North and East parts of the Lopit Mountain Range villages in the State of East Equatoria Sudan. The estimated population is 14,000. A significant investment in community vision casting was done in 2007-2008 (and re-affirmed in 2010) creating the following top priorities of enhanced community development: 
 i. Medical Care/health,
 ii. Education/Schooling for youth and,
 iii. Church Development. 
 iiii. Community Development Expertise
 v. Agricultural Development and nutrition
 vi. Micro-enterprise

 Outcomes:
 First, expected outcomes include improved health primarily in the areas of preventive and population health through training of clinic workers and regular supply of basic equipment and medications. A basic clinic facility was constructed in 2008 with a grant from AAR Japan. Volunteer medical personnel (nationals) are recruited and partially trained on basic disease identification and treatment. Training was completed by medical personnel from USA. 

 Second, in the field of education, progress has been made. The Sudanese government authorized a United Nations grant to build 3 school buildings in 2008 (prior to that time, teaching was done in the open spaces – “under the tree”). Families are encouraged to send children to school. In 2011, community leadership encouraged young girls to attend school as well (normally not done in South Sudan). In addition, a food welfare program was started to prepare one meal for the children attending school (beans and water). There is one trained teacher for the community. In 2014 (December) a community leader is expected to complete formal training at Juba University to return to the community as the ‘head teacher’ and program leader. Additional trained teachers and newer teaching methods are desired. Improved graduation from primary school (elementary school) and higher test results for secondary education (high school) are strongly held community goals. Students that can attend school in UN sanctioned border refugee camps are encouraged to do so and take advantage of more advanced curriculum. 

 Third, the community also seeks Christian development including a church building. Highland Community Church pledged to fund the church building construction and donated along with a contractual agreement were in place by 2010. A building design was rapidly completed and construction started by early 2011. Construction was completed in 2012 and a subsequent team of missionaries installed solar power to the facility. In December 2012 a community dedication ceremony launched the church for services. The building is the largest known Christian Church in South Sudan. In addition, the community requires additional trained pastors to evangelize, counsel and teach throughout the villages for the betterment of the church. Currently there is one apprentice trained pastor living in the community of 14,000. By December 2014, the first trained pastor (bachelor degree in Divinity Studies) completed training and was installed in the church. The majority of South Sudanese are nominally Christian and integration into society has aided in national identity, cultural development and more stability within South Sudan. 

 Fourth, the community has identified the need for project management and community development skills. The entire area lacks even the most basic elements of infrastructure (both physical and process/outcomes). To achieve this goal, nationals trained in program and community development, human resources management and business are needed. An ongoing effort to identify and create a community development plan with specific timelines and outcomes is identified.

 Fifth, there is a need for improved farming practices and improved nutritional practices. With limited food types and antiquated farming practices there is also a need to improve crop and animal diversity and upgrade farming techniques. Agriculture is limited to traditional/labor intensive practices and limited livestock (cattle, goats) and limited crops (ground nuts, sorghum and millet seed). Limited agricultural diversity and outdated methods leaves the community vulnerable to malnutrition, food shortages and crop/livestock disease. The desired outcome is to have one or more persons trained in agricultural methods and food sciences to improve farming practices and diet/nutrition.

 Finally, with no means of generating and sustaining wealth, the basic economy remains in a subsistence level. Early on, trainers from USA introduced the basic business practices of planning, money management and savings/loans. Using sound principles of micro-finance, an initial grant formed a rudimentary banking system that is now locally governed. A pool of capital funds are tapped for loans and terms of loan repayments are managed locally. Micro-enterprise has led to a noticed improvement in the local economy. The desired outcome is community based economy that engenders prudent risk-taking and the ability for households to move out of subsistence living.

Allah said
From The Holy Quraan : " Al-Hadid, 57vs11 "
Who is he that will lend unto Allah a goodly loan, that He may double it for him and his may be a rich reward?

The Encouragement to make a Handsome Loan in the Cause of Allah

Allah said,

مَن ذَا الَّذِي يُقْرِضُ اللَّهَ قَرْضًا حَسَنًا ...

Who is he that will lend Allah a handsome loan?

Umar bin Al-Khattab said that this Ayah refers to spending in Allah's cause.

It was also said that it pertains to spending on children.

What is correct is that it is more general than that. So all those who spend in the cause of Allah with good intentions and a sincere heart, then they fall under the generality of this Ayah. This is why Allah the Exalted said:

مَّن ذَا الَّذِي يُقْرِضُ اللّهَ قَرْضًا حَسَنًا فَيُضَاعِفَهُ لَهُ ...

Who is he that will lend Allah handsome loan: then (Allah) will increase it manifold to his credit (in repaying), and in another Ayah, أَضْعَافًا كَثِيرَةً (many times) (2:245),

meaning, being handsome reward and tremendous provisions: Paradise on the Day of Resurrection.

Ibn Abi Hatim recorded that Abdullah bin Masud said,

"When this Ayah, مَّن ذَا الَّذِي يُقْرِضُ اللّهَ قَرْضًا حَسَنًا فَيُضَاعِفَهُ لَهُ (Who is he that will lend Allah handsome loan: then (Allah) will increase it manifold to his credit (in repaying),) was revealed, Abu Ad-Dahdah Al-Ansari said, `O Allah's Messenger! Does Allah ask us for a loan' The Prophet said,

Yes, O Abu Ad-Dahdah.

He said, `Give me your hand, O Allah's Messenger,'

and the Prophet placed his hand in his hand.

Abu Ad-Dahdah said, `Verily, I have given my garden as a loan to my Lord.'

He had a garden that contained six hundred date trees; his wife and children were living in that garden too.

Abu Ad-Dahdah went to his wife and called her, Umm Ad-Dahdah!'

She said, `Here I am.'

He said, `Leave the garden, because I have given it as a loan to my Lord, the Exalted and Most Honored.'

She said, `That is a successful trade, O Abu Ad-Dahdah!'

She then transferred her goods and children.

The Messenger of Allah said,

كَمْ مِنْ عَذْقٍ رَدَاحٍ فِي الْجَنَّةِ لِأَبِي الدَّحْدَاح

How plentiful are the sweet date clusters that Abu Ad-Dahdah has in Paradise!''
